      "created": 1784801324,
      "updated": 1784801324
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61e83e00000000005a0753",
      "text": "[箇条書きのバレットをFontAwesomeにするUserCSS]では、[CSSカスタムプロパティ]（[CSS変数]）の`--ul-bullet`を用意している。このプロパティの値を書き換えればバレットの形を変更できる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1784801342,
      "updated": 1784801670
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61e84800000000005a0754",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1784801352,
      "updated": 1784801352
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61e8a900000000005a075e",
      "text": "使用例としては、[自分のページ]に次のようなUserCSSを置く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1784801449,
      "updated": 1784801771
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61e86d00000000005a0756",
      "text": "code:style.css",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1784801390,
      "updated": 1784801391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61e86e00000000005a0757",
      "text": "  :root {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1784801391,
      "updated": 1784801391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61e86e00000000005a0758",
      "text": "    --ul-bullet: '\\f005';　/* 星 */",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1784801391,
      "updated": 1784801395
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61e86e00000000005a075a",
      "text": "\t}",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1784801391,
      "updated": 1784801391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61e86e00000000005a075b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1784801391,
      "updated": 1784801391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61e88100000000005a075c",
      "text": "[箇条書きが星]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1784801410,
      "updated": 1784801446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61e88200000000005a075d",
